    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/1fd2e38c17659d14766d05ea8387885c.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=143 /></span><br><br><strong>长大成人、还是永远在一起</strong><br><br>——夏天。<br>疯狂生长着的翠绿色植物。<br>碎石路上因被阳光照耀而闪烁的白土。<br>像是庄严的城堡大门般令人生畏的积雨云。<br>更重要的是，那诡异且深不见底的蓝天。<br><br>——夏天。<br>那填满了原色的风景看起来是多么刺眼。<br>那折磨着肉体并唤起过去回忆的气候。<br>那摇曳的蜃景，映照着满满的乡愁。<br><br>——夏天。<br>孩子们最特别的季节。<br>大人们最平凡的季节。<br><br>——夏天。<br>无法重来的过去。<br><br>新年时再次相遇且半年没有见的一对青梅竹马少年亚雄与少女奇诺理，<br>逃离了无聊的亲戚聚会，两人的友宜在成熟与稚气之间摇摆…<br>没想到在寻找回家的路上不小心闯入一个名为「幽世」的村庄。<br><br>没想到那是个性别观念畸形，男女有着不对等关系的村庄。<br>因为男孩子气的外表，使村民误认为奇诺理是个男性。<br>因此，直到找到逃离村庄的方法前，两人必须想办法隐藏奇诺理是少女的事实…<br><br>村里有个绝对不能违反的规则那就是「不得伪装生理的性别」。<br>据说违反规则的人将受到极其可怕的惩罚…<br><br>究竟两人是否能顺利逃出村庄呢。<br>全部都交由玩家选择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/712be21c8d1414c285c115a7cd100215.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/ab6f6bd325cb5878db3a88303bd4d1e9.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=143 /></span><br><br><strong>体验稚气与成熟之间摆荡的青春与恋情</strong><br><br>「即使注定会相爱——即使神明期望你们能相爱——<br>　却因为命运而无法在一起，<br>　为了对抗这样的宿命，神明召唤人们来到这里。为了给予幸福的世界──」<br><br>向巫女寻求逃出方法的奇诺理与亚雄，得知了如此令人震惊的事实。<br><br>「若回到原本的世界，彼此的人生将不再重叠──」<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/90204d660de147d35b2a2b4c9aab61ef.poster.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/90204d660de147d35b2a2b4c9aab61ef.webm?t=1768896263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/90204d660de147d35b2a2b4c9aab61ef.mp4?t=1768896263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>两人将在此度过一年。<br>在这个不会衰老和死亡，且不断循环的世界中永远相爱，<br>还是克服离别，迈向未来。<br>这一切都交由玩家决定。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/677b0b0e31519e54b93a6120231a5479.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 /></span><br><br><strong>探索开放式的村庄！</strong><br><br>从早到晚，村庄中无数的事件等着你探索。<br>与奇诺理、亚雄探索这美丽且四季交错的村庄吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/ae0c975dbfc19462eca43500e7892c7d.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/86cf98c4a7656fee0a9d3199c076df88.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/d7f27c5ffec47ed64e429a6d61704f9e.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/15e45bc4e7ac3d00cb139f512ab93101.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/a9340b5346006e69535999f0e2cb6a4e.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/5ffdd6dd18bfffaf3d2d9ef0cfe4b1f9.avif?t=1768896263\" width=624 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326590/extras/12ceb21dd64552ea66b3eada9a078